49#ifndef VERSION_H_
50#define VERSION_H_ 1
51
52#ifndef NETPGP_AUTOCONF_VERSION
53#define NETPGP_AUTOCONF_VERSION PACKAGE_VERSION
54#endif
55
56#ifndef NETPGP_MAINTAINER
57#define NETPGP_MAINTAINER PACKAGE_BUGREPORT
58#endif
59
60/* development versions have .99 suffix */
61#define NETPGP_BASE_VERSION "3.99.17"
62
63#define NETPGP_VERSION_CAT(a, b) "NetPGP portable " a "/[" b "]"
64#define NETPGP_VERSION_STRING \
65 NETPGP_VERSION_CAT(NETPGP_BASE_VERSION, NETPGP_AUTOCONF_VERSION)
66
67#endif /* !VERSION_H_ */
